title: Hidden Treasures Revealed (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Hidden Treasures Revealed
Harry N. Abrams, Inc. | 1995 | ISBN: 0810934329 | English | 302 pages | PDF | 67 MB

Shows and describes French paintings that were taken from Germany to Russia at the end of World War II. The Hermitage Museum put them on show for the first time in half a century. This book displays the paintings in full colour, together with details and associated or complementary works to show their context
